cu.explanation_en: Setting remote_s_address to an invalid IP '192.168.70.256' (octet > 255) will cause connection failure in the front-haul interface, preventing proper communication between CU and DU.

du.explanation_en: Changing T1a_up from [96, 196] to [196, 96] creates timing misalignment where the upper bound is less than the lower bound, causing logical contradiction in front-haul timing parameters and potential synchronization errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將 T1a_up 從 [96, 196] 更改為 [196, 96] 會導致時序錯位，其中上限小於下限，造成前傳時序參數中的邏輯矛盾，並可能導致同步錯誤。
